data.name: Title_wellcomeWord
data.value: Thank you for using Allwin digital printer

data.name: Conten_wellcomeWord
data.value:
First --Please use allwin orginal ink： 1）the ink is environment protection and low Odor, it is stale and smoothly during printing, it can improve yield effectly and reduce the cost； 2）Prolong the lifetime of the nozzle.
Second--Machine environment requirement： ink temperature 18-27℃，air moisture40-70%，the environment without dust； 1）when the tempareture lower than 15℃，（konica）open the heating function of the sub inktank, at the same time the ink bottle can be packed by electric blanket or other heating method to make the ink temperature be 30℃, open printhead heating function(1024 machine with this function)； 2）when ink tube insert ink bottle, the hole please be smaller and the lid keep sealed to reduce the ink volatilized and prevent the dust get into it. 3 when pringt in winter, it can open spray for 10 minute to preheat( epson machine don’t need this step)； 4）please check the ink tube whether with bubble, if it has the bubble please except it firstly； 5）The picture add test bar in the two sides to prevent the nozzle clog caused by ink too less when printing.

data.name: Conten_firstPage
data.value: 1、firstly please pull up the fixed screw(konica)，the carriage move to left slowly and then seprate from bottom base. 2、move out the carriage(konica)，On the base of rubber covered with a layer of plastic wrap to prevent dust. 3 before start the machine, please check whether with some dirty things to prevent damage the print head. 4. The ink tube should without bubble or will cause to break line when printing, it needs to expel the bubble then print； 5. Please don’t let the print head leave capping and expose on the air. If the stop time is long, please set spray in the software; when the epson machine don’t use please click reset function to make capping match printhead. 6.Inkjet equipment with allwin encoder Patent configuration function , when the picture need to title please open software function operate manual to guide using encoder function so that can ensure the quality of titling.

data.name: Conten_secondPage
data.value: If the picture shows break line during printing, please deal with as following methods： 1）please abserve the surface of the head with flashlight: if find there with gathered ink please clean it with vacuum cleaner or with non-woven fabrics to rub it lightly, if don’t have gathered ink please use press ink function then press the ink will be OK. Then use non-woven fabrics to absord other ink. 2. When use the non-woven fabrics rub the printhead surface, please don’t rub one printhead back and forth, rubbing the printhead just to absorb the ink. 3 close the machine maintance, firstly, please fill cleaner into moisture base rubber on the right, move the crriage to the last right to make printhead match with moisture base completely. 4、cleaning maintance： 1、please clean the moisture base rubber and impurity. 2、please pull out the cleaner form rubber base, then clean it and fill in new cleaner every week.

data.name: Conten_thirdPage
data.value:
1.please clean the scrape in the sub inktank in every winter to prevent the ink stay at the buttom of the ink tank then cause to clog ink tube and ink head.
2.Clean moisture capping every month and clean the cleaner under the capping.
3.Clean printhead surface: when the printhead surface or two sides with dirty things, please clean the printhead surface with cleaner.
4. Feeding roller requirement：please change foam paper regularly；rub the surface of the roller
5. Please clean the ink marks on the rubber pinch roller with alcohol and Cotton silk stuff beside the pinch roller.
6. Raster bar cleaning：abserve and clean everyday; use swab adding some distilled water and alcohol to scrab dust and dirty things；
7. X,Y direction tension inspection：inspect it every three month, if it’s loosed please adjust it；
8. Please clean the abandon ink of vacuum cleaner and waste cartridge regularly.
